# Documentation Governance

**Human-readable:** [`docs/WORKFLOWS/documentation-governance.md`](../../docs/WORKFLOWS/documentation-governance.md)

## Who updates what

| File | Owner | Trigger |
|------|-------|---------|
| `docs/PROJECT_STATE.md` | Completing agent | Phase change, blocker, smoke status |
| `docs/ROADMAP.md` | Completing agent | Phase boundaries, estimates, deferrals |
| `docs/TODO.md` | Completing agent | Every task wave |
| `docs/DASHBOARD.md` | Completing agent | Status/metrics after merge wave |
| `docs/PROGRESS.md` | Completing agent | Every completed task (log entry) |
| `.context/system-plan.md` | Pontus + architect | New system phase (Fas N) |
| `docs/MODUL-FUNKTIONS-REGISTER.md` | Feature agent | New module or route |
| `docs/evaluations/*` | Audit agent | YOLO, security, large reviews |

## New system phases (Fas N)

1. Pontus approves masterplan eval (`docs/evaluations/`)
2. Update `.context/system-plan.md` with **AKTIV** marker
3. Update `docs/PROJECT_STATE.md` — agents read this first
4. Add or update program section in `docs/ROADMAP.md` if a new implementation program starts
5. Reset or branch `docs/TODO.md` for new work

## New program phases (within a Fas)

Update `docs/ROADMAP.md`, `docs/TODO.md`, `docs/DASHBOARD.md` — not `.context/system-plan.md` unless system Fas changes.

## New features

1. Check `docs/MODUL-FUNKTIONS-REGISTER.md` and GAP register
2. PMIR if locked UX, WORM, or sacred
3. Add TODO items before coding (`ide-till-kod.mdc`)

## Releases

1. `npm run smoke:predeploy:build`
2. yolo-vakt read-only audit → GO/NO-GO
3. Pontus OK
4. Deploy per `livskompassen-deploy` skill
5. `docs/PROGRESS.md` + `docs/PROJECT_STATE.md` last verified dates

## Validation

```bash
npm run smoke:governance
```
